      "description": "The Innovator U.S. Equity Buffer ETF - January (BJAN) is an exchange-traded fund that mostly invests in downside hedge alternatives. The fund aims for specific buffered losses and capped gains on the S&P 500 over a specific holdings period. The actively-managed fund holds options and collateral. BJAN was launched on Dec 31, 2018 and is issued by Innovator.",
